{"TopicId":182876,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"The Kerbin 1K Drag Race (needs Races! mod)","CreatedByName":"Triop","CreatedById":145841,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-14T22:51:43Z","PageNum":6,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jeb-head-mug kerman","CreatedById":159289,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-03T01:46:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmmm. I\u0027ll finish working on my car next week.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jacke","CreatedById":103694,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-03T02:29:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223699182\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572743521\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187168\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lisias\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Lisias said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDAMN. I have some serious work to do. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s been a while since I worked on this.\u00A0 But as I recall, I think every entry from mine down has been a Sepratron design, because nothing else has the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Thrust-to-weight ratio\u0022\u003ETWR\u003C/abbr\u003E it does.\u00A0 I tried the Vector engine and at least in my experience its designs didn\u0027t compete.\u00A0 And keeping the vehicle straight and stopping it are equal challenges.\u00A0 I think I never worked on a better one than my Rocket Sled 5 due to the shear tediousness of banking up so many Sepratrons and tweaking them to reduce their fuel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-03T02:41:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223699188\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572743724\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022159289\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jeb-head-mug kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Jeb-head-mug kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo the WHOLE car has to survive? Whoops....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the airstrip too. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0(boy, trying to remember how I managed salvage the airstrip\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Eand\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0land the cockpit on it\u2026.)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00222019-1102_Mk2-ShitHappens.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022http://ksp.lisias.net/challenges/Triops_Drag-Race-1k/2019-1102_Mk2-ShitHappens.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jacke","CreatedById":103694,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-03T08:41:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223699239\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572748881\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187168\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lisias\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Lisias said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the airstrip too. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll the sections of the airstrip too. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpeaking of KSP 1.8.1, do we need an updated Races mod?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HB Stratos","CreatedById":187428,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-07T16:06:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntime to make my own, I am still in 1.7.3 but 250 sepatrons should be plenty of boost\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HB Stratos","CreatedById":187428,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-07T20:59:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022screenshot405.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/398148589660143618/642104537485803547/screenshot405.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI came up with this unconventinal design and it has quite some power. Build in 1.7.3, untested in 1.8.1. Requires timewarp at 0.25 with better timewarp.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/398148589660143618/642104618003988480/Speeder_MkX.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/398148589660143618/642104618003988480/Speeder_MkX.craft\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0download.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nafter burnout stage and activate brakes, you\u0027ll barely have enough room.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Triop","CreatedById":145841,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-08T20:02:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223699293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572770464\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022103694\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jacke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/3/2019 at 9:41 AM, Jacke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpeaking of KSP 1.8.1, do we need an updated Races mod?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe mod is working in 1.8.1, although the loading screen says it\u0027s not.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice to see there are still gearheads on the forum. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-08T20:40:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLots and lots of inspiration. I will try the lawn mower version.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/-T04fq4W1fs?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jacke","CreatedById":103694,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-09T05:03:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223702211\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221573243374\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145841\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Triop\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Triop said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe mod is working in 1.8.1, although the loading screen says it\u0027s not.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice to see there are still gearheads on the forum. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s possible if the mod .dll used only KSP methods carefully and never went directly to Unity.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Triop","CreatedById":145841,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-09T18:12:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223702233\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221573245630\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187168\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lisias\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, Lisias said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLots and lots of inspiration. I will try the lawn mower version.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome very weird vehicles in this clip, I love it. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:lol:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_laugh.png\u0022 title=\u0022:lol:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HB Stratos","CreatedById":187428,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-10T20:20:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll make that jet car, blasting off like a rocket with burners lit\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sturmhauke","CreatedById":190611,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-10T22:19:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy stepfather would have loved that nonsense. He was\u00A0a hot rodder back in the 50s, and drove a souped-up Lincoln. One time he lost to a guy with a rusty old Hudson Terraplane that had been secretly modded with a Rolls-Royce Merlin engine, like from a Spitfire warbird.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOK so my stepfather liked to tell tall tales, so who knows if that other car really existed. But he still would have enjoyed a dragracing tractor.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-11T18:44:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223703153\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221573424393\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022190611\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sturmhauke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, sturmhauke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy stepfather would have loved that nonsense. He was\u00A0a hot rodder back in the 50s, and drove a souped-up Lincoln. One time he lost to a guy with a rusty old Hudson Terraplane that had been secretly modded with a Rolls-Royce Merlin engine, like from a Spitfire warbird.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOK so my stepfather liked to tell tall tales, so who knows if that other car really existed. But he still would have enjoyed a dragracing tractor.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe him. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/jFS83GUMTCc?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sturmhauke","CreatedById":190611,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-11T19:27:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell how about that?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LittleBitMore","CreatedById":201924,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-03-04T01:58:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis has been my favorite challenge for\u00A0\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eso long\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve finally tried to attempt it. I made a \u0022Control Buggy\u0022 which got 57 seconds. Powered entirely by rover wheels.\u00A0After many failed attempts I managed to get some embarrasing cars that either disintegrated immediately or got 6 seconds... so I\u0027ll just take my participation trophy in shame now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis won\u0027t be the last of me though! Once I\u0027m less busy I\u0027ll make a great car that gets a score higher than\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eat least\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0one person.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EIn the name of the Holly Kerbol that Enlighten us all, I claim my rightful place as (eternal) 3rd\u00A0on the Scoreboard.\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 style=\u0022border-style:none;vertical-align:middle;\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/187168-lisias/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022187168\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/187168-lisias/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Lisias\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0, I was inspired by your design and tried to attempt a functional unpowered glider escape system that would loop around and parachute over the runway. It never got through the race before disintegrating, but by my estimates it would\u0027ve gotten around 4 seconds. The wings wrapped around the 1.25m wide thruster stage. I did however test it on a pitifully slow stage that did the run in 8 seconds, and it glided well enough back to the runway. I hope you can forge something excellent using both my knowledge and your knowledge.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LittleBitMore","CreatedById":201924,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-03-04T22:05:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI made something go moderately fast. Only problems: instability, escape system, and Race ignores the fast it got past the end.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll keep you posted with edits.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-edit-\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell that didn\u0027t work. I never managed to make it stable enough. The time it happened to fly through the gate it got something like 3.5 seconds, but since it really didn\u0027t survive, I wouldn\u0027t count on sending it to anyone.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve been trying some weird designs with angled radial engines that thrust the car into the ground, as well as spinning BreakingGround motorized launchers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-edit-\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve developed a new line of amazing drag racers that make the leaderboards! The Airplanen\u0027t racers have peaked at 3.78 seconds. I\u0027m making a KerbalX file for the Mk1 design now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-03-04T22:58:21Z\u0022 title=\u002203/04/2020 10:58  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 4, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by LittleBitMore\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EEdits\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LittleBitMore","CreatedById":201924,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-03-04T23:11:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI present to you: the \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/LittleBitMore/Airplanent-Mk1\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EAirplanen\u0027t Mk1\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAgainst popular belief, this craft does not fly like an airplane. Any attempts to do so result in your warranty becoming void. Instead, it blazes through the 1km sprint at a blistering time of\u00A0\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E3.78 s\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll make something better soon. I am now employing a great trick if you need extra stability: hold shift, offset wheels, add struts, and pretend it\u0027s legal. This trick was pilfered from \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/152460-swjr-swis/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022152460\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/152460-swjr-swis/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@swjr-swis\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInstructions:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nActivate \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThrottle up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake sure Races is on.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHit space.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDO NOT TOUCH until flamout.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIMMEDIATELY hit space.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSuccess!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: tested and\u00A0\u003Cs\u003Eflown\u003C/s\u003E rolled in 1.9.1. Races surprisingly still works!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022agg5jQa.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/agg5jQa.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022p0Qnhdg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/p0Qnhdg.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022YzPoIST.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/YzPoIST.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-03-04T23:15:49Z\u0022 title=\u002203/04/2020 11:15  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 4, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by LittleBitMore\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eadded edit\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LittleBitMore","CreatedById":201924,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-03-05T20:32:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGuess what?\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/LittleBitMore/Airplanent-Mk2\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EAirplanen\u0027t Mk2\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0is what!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt gets through the course in various times under 3.05s, once going\u00A0\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E2.98s\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E! This was tested and \u003Cs\u003Eflown\u003C/s\u003E\u00A0rolled in 1.9.1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPowered by huge amounts of Vectors and held together by bucketloads of struts, this one is actually capable of flight (but this normally ends in fire and death, so your warranty will still be voided if this is attempted).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWARNING: Survival is pretty fifty fifty. The below instructions MIGHT help you survive.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBefore you launch, as SOON as the vessel loads, throttle up, enable stability assist, and start the Races! timer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStage.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022dOh2rAZ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/dOh2rAZ.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKeep it in the center of the runway with A and D.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are tons of fins especially for this purpose. Too little control and it falls over onto the grass and misses the gate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022FTnuwT5.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/FTnuwT5.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn flameout, pull up and then \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003ENEARLY\u00A0INSTANTLY\u00A0\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003Estage. Otherwise your kerbal will probably die.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoing W too early will flip it over and kill your kerbal and doing space too early will smear your kerbal into the tarmac.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnce you stage, just to be sure it does it correctly, spam space.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022rBXasKI.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/rBXasKI.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKeep the escape thrusters from thrusting directly down until the chutes deploy, if possible. (Upwards thrusters were necessary to prevent kerbal smearage.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022WJRNgz1.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/WJRNgz1.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSuccess!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022JFtZJLY.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/JFtZJLY.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Ignore that random FAT-455 airplane fin flying in the background.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVideo of 3.02s run:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/iZdmt8Q.mp4\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://i.imgur.com/iZdmt8Q.mp4\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope you enjoy my entry! Honestly I\u0027m just glad I finally got up the ranks a little.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-03-29T16:15:57Z\u0022 title=\u002203/29/2020 04:15  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 29, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by LittleBitMore\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdded video, edited instructions for lowering mortality rate\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}